from time import time
from contextlib import contextmanager
from functools import wraps

def timer(func):

    @wraps(func)
    def wrapper(*args, **kwargs):
        start_time = time()
        result = func(*args, **kwargs)
        end_time = time()
        print(f'{(end_time - start_time) * 1000} ms')
        return result
    return wrapper
